function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(id_Artair) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_Artair_Start,  id_Artair)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(id_Artair, marker_Artair_RunToRitual, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(id_Artair, marker_Artair_RunToRitual)
	end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	
	-- Remove tether and play effect on ritual items
	Hydra.QActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(id_Artair, effect_Rope_Shadow)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(id_Artair)
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(marker_GoatBlood_Location, effect_Buff_Shadow)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(marker_WolfBlood_Location, effect_Buff_Shadow)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(id_WolfTotem_SP, effect_Buff_Shadow)
end

	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_Artair_Ritual, id_Artair)
	
	
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	id_Goat_Blood = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(marker_GoatBlood_Location, marker_Una_Location, effect_Rope_Shadow, true)
	id_Wolf_Blood = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(marker_WolfBlood_Location, marker_Una_Location, effect_Rope_Shadow, true)
	id_Totem = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(id_WolfTotem_SP, marker_Una_Location, effect_Rope_Shadow, true)
	
	-- Presentation for summoning Una
	id_BloodGlob = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(marker_Una_Location, effect_Burst_Shadow, true)
	Hydra.Wait(4.0)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(id_Una)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(id_Una, power_Una_Taunt)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_Una_Bark, id_Una)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(marker_GoatBlood_Location, id_Goat_Blood)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(marker_WolfBlood_Location, id_Wolf_Blood)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(id_WolfTotem_SP, id_Totem)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(marker_Una_Location)
	
	-- Add tether from Artair to Una
	id_Tether = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(id_Artair, id_Una, effect_Rope_Shadow, true)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(id_Artair, marker_Artair_RunToExit, "npc_run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(id_Artair, 1.0)
end
